name: Darla Smith
text: We had buffet.  Always plenty of food.  If anything ran out it was soon replaced.  Nice variety of pizza, pasta, desserts, salad.  It was very busy, but waitress took good care of us.  Very friendly.

text: Fantastic lunch buffet we went on a Saturday arrived close to tear down time an they left it up longer for us! Wasn't expecting that at all!! My Mom had been craving Pizza Hut buffet for a couple years an they didn't disappoint!! :) Thank you so much!

name: Virginia Mosel
text: Watch your receipts when doing their Wednesday night wing deal, .50 cents a wing. We got 8 wings and charged $4.80. 8x.50 cents =$4. And one of the chicken pieces was raw (so only 7 edible ones). They said they have never had anyone ask them about this before.
